+        `Adjusted OLS coefficient for nlr_z was ${fmtNumber(baseModel.terms.nlr_z.estimate)} months per SD (p=${fmtP(baseModel.terms.nlr_z.p)}).`,
+        termResult(baseModel, "nlr_z"),
+        "OLS: pfs_months ~ standardized nlr + clinical covariates + biomarkers + treatments",
