+        `Adjusted OLS coefficient for stage_iv was ${fmtNumber(baseModel.terms.stage_iv.estimate)} months (p=${fmtP(baseModel.terms.stage_iv.p)}), indicating shorter PFS after adjustment for demographics, performance status, inflammatory labs, biomarkers, and treatments.`,
+        termResult(baseModel, "stage_iv"),
+        "OLS: pfs_months ~ stage_iv + age_years + sex_female + brain mets + ECOG + labs + biomarkers + treatments",
+      ),
+      analysisRecord(
