+        `Adjusted OLS coefficient for tmb_high was ${fmtNumber(baseModel.terms.tmb_high.estimate)} months (p=${fmtP(baseModel.terms.tmb_high.p)}).`,
+        termResult(baseModel, "tmb_high"),
+        "OLS: pfs_months ~ tmb_high + clinical covariates + biomarkers + treatments",
