I found two strong prognostic lab/cachexia signals that are more informative than the initial CRP/NLR hypotheses, so I’m replacing that iteration with LDH and 6-month weight loss. I’m also removing a bad PD-L1 threshold check that produced `NaN` because this dataset stores PD-L1 on a smaller numeric scale.
