+        `Adjusted OLS coefficient for spo2_pct_z was ${fmtNumber(broadMainModel.terms.spo2_pct_z.estimate)} months per SD (p=${fmtP(broadMainModel.terms.spo2_pct_z.p)}).`,
+        termResult(broadMainModel, "spo2_pct_z"),
+        "Broad OLS: pfs_months ~ standardized spo2_pct + clinical covariates + biomarkers + treatments",
+      ),
+      analysisRecord(
