+        `Adjusted OLS coefficient for heart_rate_bpm_z was ${fmtNumber(broadMainModel.terms.heart_rate_bpm_z.estimate)} months per SD (p=${fmtP(broadMainModel.terms.heart_rate_bpm_z.p)}).`,
+        termResult(broadMainModel, "heart_rate_bpm_z"),
+        "OLS: pfs_months ~ standardized heart_rate_bpm + clinical covariates + biomarkers + treatments",
+      ),
