+        `For treatment_osimertinib, the unadjusted treatment-only coefficient was ${fmtNumber(treatmentOnlyModel.terms.treatment_osimertinib.estimate)} months (p=${fmtP(treatmentOnlyModel.terms.treatment_osimertinib.p)}), while the adjusted main-effect coefficient was ${fmtNumber(baseModel.terms.treatment_osimertinib.estimate)} months (p=${fmtP(baseModel.terms.treatment_osimertinib.p)}), showing sensitivity to covariate and biomarker adjustment.`,
+        {
